Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:04.82,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,fx,我爱你 这样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:08.92,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,fx,还是初次体会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:10.12,op-cn,,0000,0000,0000,,哦~哦~
